==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Induplicate
<hw>In*du"pli*cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>Having the edges bent abruptly toward the axis; --
said of the parts of the calyx or corolla in ⟦ae⟧stivation.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>Having the edges rolled inward and then arranged about
the axis without overlapping; -- said of leaves in vernation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Induplicative</ent>⟦br⟧
